OL,6,FA man from Gloucester has been been
OL,7,Fsentenced to 22 years in prison after
OL,8,Fhe preyed on vulnerable young men he
OL,9,Fhad met through gay support charities.
OL,11,FTimothy Darch, of Southrop Road
OL,12,FKingsway, Quedgeley, was sentenced on
OL,13,F28 March at Swindon Crown Court after
OL,14,Fbeing found guilty by trial in
OL,15,FFebruary.
OL,17,FThe 62-year-old was sentenced for four
OL,18,Fcounts of rape on a boy under the age
OL,19,Fof 16, and four counts of indecent
OL,20,Fassault on a boy under the age of 16.
