OL,10,F'No amount of justice can give me back
OL,11,Fwhat I have lost'
OL,13,FIn a statement read to the court one
OL,14,Fof his victim's said: "I was a child
OL,15,Fwhen I met Tim, so manipulating me and
OL,16,Fsexualising and abusing me was easy
OL,17,Ffor him. The damage he has done to me
OL,18,Fhas affected my whole life.
