OL,6,F"He played various mind games and was
OL,7,Fvery good at manipulating me and
OL,8,Fothers to get whatever he wanted.
OL,10,F"I came forward as I was worried he
OL,11,Fwas subjecting others to abuse like he
OL,12,Fdid me. I wish I had the strength to
OL,13,Fcome forward sooner, but this has
OL,14,Ftaken so much strength from me to get
OL,15,Fthis far.
OL,17,F"I am aware that no amount of justice
OL,18,Fwill ever give me back what I have
OL,19,Flost, I am however hoping that I can
OL,20,Fget some sort of closure from all of
OL,21,Fthis."
