OL,6,FDetective Constable Ross Duff, from
OL,7,FSwindon CID, said: "Darch met the
OL,8,Fyoung men through Swindon
OL,9,Forganisations such as support
OL,10,Fcharities for young gay men.
OL,12,F"Darch put himself in a position of
OL,13,Ftrust and exploited and took advantage
OL,14,Fof those vulnerable children.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank his victims for
OL,17,Ftheir incredible bravery throughout
OL,18,Fthis process, by giving their evidence
OL,19,Fto police and throughout the trial.
